text: The Fiji Women's Pro 2015 was an event of the Association of Surfing Professionals for 2015 ASP World Tour. This event was held from 01 to 5 June at Namotu, (Tavarua, Fiji) and opposed by 36 surfers. The tournament was won by Sally Fitzgibbons (AUS), who beat B.
